p: Based on this correlation study, we noticed that six components were present only in our essential oil, namely bicyclosesquiphellandrene (5.6%), α-amorphene (5.1%), 2,3-dihydro-1,8-cineole (2%), limonene (0.5%), and 2,3-di- tert-butylphenol (0.5%). In addition, for bicyclogermacrene (5.0%) and ( E)-β-ocimene (2.4%), the correlation has not been established because we did not have enough data (only two essential oils).
